chunk_content: It is vital that facility level data collection and program monitoring tools capture the data elements necessary to identify this key performance issue, which can lead to data quality issues for this indicator. How to review for The numerator for this indicator should not be larger than CXCA_SCRN and should be equal to 100% data quality: or less of the CXCA_SCRN_POS disaggregate (not including suspected cancer). How to calculate Sum results across both reporting periods for the numerator.
